{"word":"H1902 - הִגָּיֹון - higgâyôwn - hig-gaw-yone' - Device","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">הִגָּיֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>higgâyôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hig-gaw-yone'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Device"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தியானம், ஆனந்த சத்தம், யோசனை, - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a meditation, resounding music, a musing"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Intensive from <a href=\"#/H1897 - הָגָה - hâgâh - daw-gaw'/1897\">H1897</a>; a <i>murmuring</i> sound, that is, a musical notation (probably similar to the moder <i>affettuoso</i> to indicate solemnity of movement); by implication a <i>machination: - </i>device, Higgaion, meditation, solemn sound."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1897 - הָגָה - hâgâh - daw-gaw'/1897\">H1897</a>, <a href=\"#/H1899 - הֶגֶה - hegeh - heh'-geh/1899\">H1899</a>, <a href=\"#/H1900 - הָגוּת - hâgûwth - haw-gooth'/1900\">H1900</a>, <a href=\"#/H1902 - הִגָּיֹון - higgâyôwn - hig-gaw-yone'/1902\">H1902</a>"}]}